  "logNo": "220126746184",
  "title": "남한산성 행궁과 북문",
  "addDate": "2014. 9. 19.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220126746184",
  "html_size": 183513,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220126746184\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220126746184\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>하늘을 보니 가을이 맞나 봅니다.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>봄부터 여름내 뿌옇던 하늘이 쨍하니 맑아졌네요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>날씨가 너무 좋아서 나들이 가기로 합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_50/isuhani_14111106680957YpXm_JPEG/IMG_0389.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_50/isuhani_14111106680957YpXm_JPEG/IMG_0389.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_50/isuhani_14111106680957YpXm_JPEG/IMG_0389.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>7-8년 전에 방문했을 때보다 </p><p>많이 바뀌었더군요</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>일단 지도를 보고 지리를 파악해봅니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_296/isuhani_141111044510777av7_JPEG/IMG_0493.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_296/isuhani_141111044510777av7_JPEG/IMG_0493.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_296/isuhani_141111044510777av7_JPEG/IMG_0493.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>행궁을 먼저 방문합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>여기는 입장료가 있네요. </p><p>성인 2천원. </p><p>미취학아동 무료.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_223/isuhani_1411110444423HfP4R_JPEG/IMG_0470.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_223/isuhani_1411110444423HfP4R_JPEG/IMG_0470.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_223/isuhani_1411110444423HfP4R_JPEG/IMG_0470.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>날씨가 정말 좋더군요. </p><p>1년의 반만 이런 날씨였다면 정말 좋겠어요.</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d0ebb51c95fe1b0.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_152/isuhani_1411110444662XXLJu_JPEG/IMG_0471.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d0ebb51c95fe1b0.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>나무도 푸르고</p><p>하늘도 푸르고</p><p>..</p><p>사실은 나무는 초록이고</p><p>하늘은 파랑이고 ^^</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d7129247455dcdef.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_143/isuhani_14111104448762Xm6i_JPEG/IMG_0482.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d7129247455dcdef.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>날씨가 맑으니 모든 색들이 더 도드라져 보입니다.</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10e1efffc403bfd1.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_2/isuhani_1411110445761leJLL_JPEG/IMG_0495.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/10e1efffc403bfd1.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>담장 밑 호박.</p><p>호박잎 틈으로 호박꽃과 호박열매가 언듯 보이네요.</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2b8a83e6a6133d62.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_269/isuhani_14111104459386YL2z_JPEG/IMG_0498.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2b8a83e6a6133d62.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>오늘은 나들이 온거니까. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>남한산성 한바퀴 돌기... 는 못하고</p><p>가까운 북문을 거점으로 잠깐 산책하기로 합니다. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>북문까지는 가깝네요.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_292/isuhani_1411110446185qTftQ_JPEG/IMG_0526.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 366px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140919_292/isuhani_1411110446185qTftQ_JPEG/IMG_0526.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003340939648')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140919_292/isuhani_1411110446185qTftQ_JPEG/IMG_0526.JPG?type=w3\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>산성을 따라 산책하면서 보는 </p><p>하늘</p><p>나무</p><p>먼 산</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>참 좋네요. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" />&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
